{"tid":1084657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊緣人也能開心離職！日業者推超溫暖「單人歡送趴」","createTime":"2019-03-30T14:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T15:08:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e86132c412823b9da384388a01bc130f5010e92","tid":1084657,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"日本新財政年度是從4月開始，因此3月常有離職潮。日本一間餐廳最近推出「單人送別會」套餐組合，不管是在公司有多邊緣的人，都能有場歡送趴。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，日本關西連鎖餐廳「ごちそう村」的20家門市最近推出「單人送別會」組合，除了有生魚片、燒牛肉、甜點等美食，店裡的工作人員還會假裝成你同事，準備花束、卡片來歡送、並一起乾杯慶祝。而且甜點還會用巧克力醬寫上「感謝你的辛苦工作」。<br />\n<br />\n店家表示，他們過去曾遇過客人面臨退休，但卻沒有人幫他舉辦告別派對，因此讓他們意識到這樣的市場需求，所以策劃了這樣的活動。這項套餐的價格約在4000到5000元日幣（約1100到1400元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZTXppf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZTXppf.jpg&h=a7853e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php8qpFbg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php8qpFbg.jpg&h=5e960b4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a10a87b5a9086a938abc89aae848fca6f904b87d","tid":1084657,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:49:15.000Z","msg":"又賺一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cdb459bb3d876c010e29e97052a95fe14121d9","tid":1084657,"uid":151539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣同自己呃自己有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dbd4726c3079f147af690c67a4e2c9909178e3","tid":1084657,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ad3f953ba0058347d8253a739675971ef8596ea","tid":1084657,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65dbd4726c3079f147af690c67a4e2c9909178e3","ti